Description (kopieer dit):

NostrComments adds a fully decentralized, censorship-resistant comment section to any website using the Nostr protocol.

Features
• Works on every site (nu.nl, YouTube, Reddit, Twitter…)
• Connect with Alby, nos2x, GetAlby, etc.
• Up/downvotes, search, sorting, pagination
• No servers, no moderation, no deletion — ever
• 100% open source (MIT)

Categories: Social & Communication + Privacy & Security
License: MIT License
Source code: https://github.com/JOUWUSERNAME/NostrComments

